# 高德地图_搜索框热词
http-response ^https?:\/\/.*\.amap\.com\/ws\/shield\/search\/new_hotword script-path=https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ddgksf2013/Scripts/refs/heads/master/amap.js, requires-body=true, tag=高德搜索热词

